{"tid":749911,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"偷100萬輸光被捕 咁點解唔偷夠1500萬？","createTime":"2018-07-20T12:09:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T12:47:17.000Z","uid":67356,"like":17,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"970e28d646747db0542c9bdf5e8b2f0e4101a7cb","tid":749911,"uid":67356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T12:09:12.000Z","msg":"假設目標係賺100萬還債同準備結婚<br />\n偷100萬賭一鋪大細有大約50%機會贏200萬，可以還返100萬比銀行，再拎100萬重啟人生；亦有50%機會輸，還唔返筆錢，比人發現虧空然後坐監<br />\n<br />\n如果偷1500萬，用倍數下注法，只有6.25%機會連輸4局，結果同樣還唔起坐監；但就有93%機會賺100萬<br />\n<br />\n以上前提係佢係一個優秀嘅魔術師，偷1500萬甚至更多都唔會比人發現<br />\n如果唔係就要計埋偷錢同還錢嘅風險，乘埋賭博嘅概率先至知道風險有幾大<br />\n<br />\n如果我係銀行經理兼魔術師，又欠債40萬，仲要比人逼婚等用錢，話唔定都會搏一鋪，九成機會賺一百萬喎"},{"pid":"2ec6ef19ff88bd78c08f1d6abdb4ab81979299ea","tid":749911,"uid":3698,"like":94,"dislike":4,"score":90,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T12:19:18.000Z","msg":"以上前提係佢係一個優秀嘅魔術師，偷1500萬甚至更多都唔會比人發現<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你不如前提佢係賭俠，問人借廿蚊就得啦戇鳩"},{"pid":"4643750140cd6b3573405c36883fb5a47e0940d0","tid":749911,"uid":7840,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T12:22:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"14f0d4b0e51a52411ec9d9bc4cc3d8377a5e671b","tid":749911,"uid":41737,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T12:23:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f86259afacbcea6d895c8ec547d771e412f5e051","tid":749911,"uid":1247,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T12:34:10.000Z","msg":"孖葉都偷埋你 咁咪無野塔到我囉? 咁偷幾多錢又有咩所謂"},{"pid":"54f196ccbb6651ae8778d71e8ec6cf22f91f4339","tid":749911,"uid":12828,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"repl